20:["$","section",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":["If you are a UK tradesperson — ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/ai-call-answering-plumbers","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"plumber"}],", ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/ai-call-answering-electricians","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"electrician"}],", ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/ai-call-answering-roofers","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"roofer"}],", ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/ai-call-answering-locksmiths","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"locksmith"}],", gas engineer,",["$","a",null,{"href":"/ai-call-answering-builders","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"builder"}],", ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/ai-call-answering-landscapers","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"landscaper"}],", or any trade that works with your hands — you have a phone problem. The Office for National Statistics (ONS) reports that ",["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-white","children":"62% of calls to small UK trade businesses go unanswered"}],". Of those missed callers, 85% never ring back. They simply call the next number on Google."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":["The financial impact is staggering. A typical sole trader loses an estimated ",["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-white","children":"£5,200 to £25,000+ per year"}]," in missed revenue, depending on trade and average job value. For emergency trades like plumbing and locksmithing, where a single emergency callout can be worth £150–£400, the cost of one missed call per day exceeds £50,000 annually."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":"AI call answering has emerged as the practical, affordable solution. What began as basic voicemail replacements has evolved into sophisticated revenue capture systems that answer every call 24/7, qualify leads, capture customer details, and deliver enquiries instantly to your WhatsApp. For tradespeople who cannot stop mid-job to answer a phone, AI call answering is not a luxury — it is essential business infrastructure."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":["This guide covers everything: what AI call answering is, how the technology works, real pricing, which trades benefit most, how it compares to human receptionists and voicemail, and exactly how to set it up in 30 minutes. For a detailed look at round-the-clock service, see our ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/blog/247-call-answering-uk-trades-guide-2026","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"24/7 call answering guide"}],". For pricing specifics, check our ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/blog/ai-call-answering-pricing-guide-uk-2026","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"AI call answering pricing guide"}],". All data is verified from ONS, Federation of Small Businesses (FSB), and our own independent testing."]}]]}]}]
