52:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"For builders and roofers with higher job values, the returns are extraordinary. A builder missing one extension enquiry per month (£40,000 average value, 30% conversion) loses £144,000/year in potential revenue. Capturing even 10% of these via AI pays for decades of service costs."}]
